PROJECT: Build the full production website for DONNA – The AI Office Assistant.
This website replaces the prelaunch landing page and will serve as Donna’s main public-facing SaaS platform.

OBJECTIVE FOR TRAYCER

Create a complete development plan, including:

Full site architecture

Page-by-page structure and content outlines

Component list

UX flow

API + integration considerations

SEO strategy

Suggested technology stack for front-end + CMS

Wireframe description for each page

Prioritized build phases (MVP → Beta → Full Release)

