3. TECHNICAL & DESIGN REQUIREMENTS

Tell Traycer to plan for:

Frontend

Next.js (recommended)

TailwindCSS

React Server Components

Vercel hosting

CMS options: Sanity, Contentful, or Strapi

Backend (if required)

API endpoints (for docs, KB previews, demos)

Analytics tracking

SEO metadata automation

Internationalization support (English → Spanish → Mandarin future)

UI/UX Guidelines

Modern SaaS aesthetic

Clean white + purple accents (Donna brand)

Bento-grid component sections

Animated transitions for product demos

Mobile-first responsive design

Option for dark mode

